---
import Section from "../ui/Section.astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import shakirPortrait from "../../assets/images/shakir-portrait.webp";
---

<Section id="about" variant="black">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 md:gap-24 items-center">
        <!-- Left: Image -->
        <div class="order-2 md:order-1 relative reveal">
            <div
                class="absolute inset-0 border border-brand-gold/20 transform -translate-x-4 translate-y-4"
            >
            </div>
            <Image
                src={shakirPortrait}
                alt="Portrait of Shakir, founder of By Shakir luxury interior design studio"
                width={800}
                height={1000}
                loading="lazy"
                decoding="async"
                class="relative z-10 w-full h-auto transition-all duration-700 object-cover aspect-[4/5]"
            />
        </div>

        <!-- Right: Content -->
        <div class="order-1 md:order-2 reveal">
            <p
                class="text-brand-gold text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-4"
            >
                The Origin
            </p>
            <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-heading mb-8 leading-tight">
                Not a Furniture Store. <br />
                <span class="text-brand-text/50">A Design Authority.</span>
            </h2>

            <div class="space-y-6 text-brand-text/80 leading-relaxed">
                <p>
                    "I noticed a gap. The local market was flooded with
                    retailers selling products, not visions. They offered
                    furniture. I wanted to offer a lifestyle."
                </p>
                <p>
                    By Shakir was born from a desire to bring the "International
                    Hotel Vibe" to the Gelderland region. Merging the brutalist
                    elegance of Dubai architecture with the warmth of high-end
                    hospitality, we create spaces that don't just look
                    expensiveâ€”they feel important.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-8 flex items-center space-x-4">
                <div class="h-px w-12 bg-brand-gold"></div>
                <span class="font-heading text-xl italic text-brand-gold"
                    >Shakir</span
                >
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</Section>
